locality: Rancho El Jabalí, 22 km (airline) N of Colima in the SW foothills of the Volcan de Colima, Colima/Jalisco line passes through ranch. Near the turnoff to Lago Jabalí on the main rach road from headquarters to Lago Epazote
La Joya area of Rancho El Jabali, 22 km NNW of the city of Colima. Volcanic area with clay soils on steep slopes and alluvial flats; the vegetation predominantly humid montane (cloud) forest.
